      "title": "SABINE ROYALTY TRUST ANNOUNCES MONTHLY CASH DISTRIBUTION FOR MAY 2026",
      "summary": "Sabine Royalty Trust (NYSE: SBR) declared a cash distribution of $0.497900 per unit for May 2026, payable on May 29, 2026. The distribution reflects February 2026 oil production of 56,677 barrels at $60.97/barrel and January 2026 gas production of 1,220,056 Mcf at $3.98/Mcf. This month's distribution increased compared to the prior month due to higher oil and natural gas prices and increased production volumes.",
